summary: An ordinance providing for the laying off, opening, widening, extending, and establishing of Airport Way from Norfolk Street to the south city limits of the City of Seattle, and Norfolk Street from Airport Way westerly; providing for the condemnation, appropriation, taking and damaging of land and other property necessary therefor, and for the making of the necessary slopes for cuts and fills upon the property abutting on said Norfolk Street; providing that the entire cost of said improvement shall be paid from the City Street Fund and declaring an emergency.
